@startuml Simulation_Challenge_States

' ============================================
' STATE DIAGRAM: Simulation Challenge Lifecycle
' Bug Bounty and Its Simulation Platform
' ============================================

title Simulation Challenge State Transitions

[*] --> Available : Challenge published

Available --> Started : Researcher starts challenge
Started --> In_Progress : Instance deployed
In_Progress --> Paused : Researcher pauses
Paused --> In_Progress : Resume challenge

In_Progress --> Submitted : Solution submitted
Submitted --> Evaluating : Auto-grading
Evaluating --> Passed : Score >= 70%
Evaluating --> Failed : Score < 70%

Passed --> Completed : Challenge complete
Failed --> Retry_Available : Retry allowed
Retry_Available --> In_Progress : Retry attempt
Retry_Available --> Abandoned : No retry

Completed --> [*]
Abandoned --> [*]

note right of In_Progress
  Active session:
  - Vulnerable app running
  - Timer active
  - Hints available (max 3)
end note

note right of Evaluating
  Scoring criteria:
  - Exploit correctness (60%)
  - Description quality (30%)
  - Time taken (10%)
end note

note right of Passed
  Rewards:
  - Points earned
  - Badge unlocked
  - Next level access
end note

@enduml